<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="02 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正在讀著從圖書館借來的
推理小說，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />發現小說裡夾著一張便條紙。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="2" arg="0x3 0x7 0x8 0x9" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="04 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我緊張地看了看那張便條紙，<delay20 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然看到便條紙上寫著犯人的名字！<delay8 />
我小說才讀到一半……</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0x5 0x6" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得很不甘心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />於是我就寫上自己的名字，<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />重新把便條紙夾了回去，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />紙上寫的是真的嗎？<delay20 />我心存懷疑地
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一直讀到最後，<delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然真的是犯人的名字，我好失望，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛好讀到一段<delay8 />
描寫犯人把便條紙夾進書裡的場景，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我嚇了一大跳！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，仔細一看，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這張便條紙原來只是一張購物清單而已，<delay8 />
我好傻眼，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我抱著緊張的心情，繼續讀下去，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果發現便條紙裡寫著<delay frames="40" />
「氣球就算被蚊子叮到，也不會破掉。」
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我實在太在意那張便條紙，<delay20 />
小說的內容反倒<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都讀不進腦袋裡了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我抱著緊張的心情，繼續讀下去，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果發現便條紙上寫著<delay frames="40" />
「企鵝是不會凍傷的。」<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得自己好像變聰明了點，<delay20 />
於是就跑去把這件事
告訴<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" />了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="0b 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說我常常會
用<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />來做蛋糕！</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xc 0xd 0xe" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果配上奶茶一起享用，<delay20 />
就會非常好吃喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是我都會不小心吃太多，<delay20 />
結果肚子撐得連走路都走不動<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抵抗不了自己做的蛋糕的誘惑……<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這正是我最近的煩惱呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，如果一直做相同的東西，<delay20 />
果然還是會膩呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次我想模仿幸運餅乾，
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在蛋糕裡放入籤詩<delay20 />
再拿去烤烤看。
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
要是烤成功的話，<delay8 />希望你可以來吃喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />除此之外，<delay20 />我有時候也會
用<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />來製作果汁喔。<pageBreak />我研究了各種<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />做得好吃的方法呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是我開發出新的食譜，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請務必來試吃看看喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x10 0x11 0x12" /></message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說，我想讓自己的
編織技術更加精進呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以前我雖然對編織不拿手，<delay20 />
但是埋頭編著編著，
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就越來越樂在其中了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來我或許滿擅長這種<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要一步步埋頭苦幹的事，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說我最近<delay20 />
開始迷上了編織呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一開始，<delay20 />我嘗試替喜歡的布偶<delay8 />
織了一條圍巾<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但好像織得太短，讓布偶有點難受呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說我最近<delay20 />
對編織非常熱衷喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />起先我試著織了一個
簡單的杯墊，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用在喝果汁的時候非常方便呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我後來織得太起勁，<delay20 />
結果杯墊變得比杯子還多了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="65 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a">我在日常生活當中，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就相當堅持親筆寫字喔。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然最近也有很多數位型記事本，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但原始的方式<delay8 />
還是有它獨特的優點呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是把自己期待的行程寫進記事本，<delay8 />
我就會覺得興奮起來喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且事後再回顧內容也很開心，<delay20 />
所以以前的記事本<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />全都是<delay8 />我的寶物！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">最近就算是上班族，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />似乎也有很多人不用記事本了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為萬用手冊的重量很重，<delay20 />
所以如果要隨身攜帶的話，<delay8 />
我也是選用小型的記事本。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我想，<delay20 />
或許能把行程完全記在腦中<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才是最好的吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="66 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我實在很喜歡文具，<delay20 />
光是看著它們，
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就覺得心情很雀躍呢<tag a="110" b="0" />！</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實，<delay8 />我很喜歡收集鋼筆，<delay20 />
所以收藏了很多喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />墨水隨著在紙上滑動的鋼筆，<delay8 />
流暢地流至筆尖，<delay20 />
這種感覺真是讓人上癮呢，<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像我自己就是因為一支鉛筆，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而開始喜歡文具用品的喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那支鉛筆的筆芯強度，<delay20 />
還有書寫的手感<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是讓我感動不已呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實文具中也有很多<delay20 />
貴得讓人買不下手的高價品喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以別太過於沉迷其中<delay20 />
或許比較不傷荷包呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是我很久以前
買過一支漂亮的原子筆，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它可是要價<colour id="1" />50000鈴錢<colour id="65535" />呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0x14 0x15" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x17 0x18 0x19" /></message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="026_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個～<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
原來你是在<tag a="135" b="4" arg="0xcd00" />界<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />持續寫出暢銷曲的大師嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思，<delay20 />
我對音樂界不太了解<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />不是嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也真是的，難道是我聽錯了嗎？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是對不起，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />你以前是不是<delay8 />
曾經在<tag a="135" b="8" arg="0xcd00" />的世界大賽上贏得優勝，<delay8 />
還因此上過電視呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實第一次見面的時候，<delay8 />
我就覺得好像在哪裡看過你喔～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那時候的冠軍訪談<delay8 />果然是<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />抱歉，<delay frames="30" />是我認錯人了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過如果是你的話，<delay8 />從現在就開始特訓，<delay8 />
說不定也能贏得優勝喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="027" attrib="1c 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay20 />我有事情<delay8 />
很想跟<tag a="110" b="4" />說喔。<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是什麼事呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！</message>
	<message label="028" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x1d 0x1e 0x1f" /></message>
	<message label="029" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我夢到我跟<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
在比賽<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比得勝負難分呢～
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然最後是我輸了，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我下次會贏的。<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們下次<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再在夢裡玩吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我夢到我跟<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
在玩<tag a="135" b="8" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超開心的～
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在最後道別之前，<delay8 />我就醒來了。<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果夢到後續，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們再一起玩<tag a="135" b="8" arg="0xcd00" />吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還是想不起來。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對不起！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然讓你花時間<delay8 />
在這種事情上，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>